{
  "stem": "18626.10",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That would be-- people were wishing in the camps just to punch one of these guys in the nose and then die.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That kind of wish they used they have in the camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have the opportunity like that, if I can-- if I'm going to be, be able to go through with the interview and be selected, I would-- I would thank God.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would fall on my knees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was interviewed by the two-- I think they were, if I don't mistake-- captains, maybe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are two, here-- maybe the captains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were, like, assistant, you know, prosecutors to the American, you know, tribunal.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because in Dachau, the trial was not by civilians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was by the American government.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was American Army-- government trial, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they start to ask me certain questions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- the last three, four months in Dachau, I was working already in the barrack their mechanics, you know, work in German mechanics.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We are building, you know, for the Messerschmitt, all kind of munitions, you know, and parts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were building-- they, they were all the time saying, the Germans, in that place, it used to be called, 'Moll.' Moll was called that place where they were building the big factories.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, here, we are going to build the secret weapon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they are going to wipe out America to the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what used to say every day the Germans to me because I was working in the same place where they were working.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They needed a woodturner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One time they came while we were-- came from the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we are still in the lines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Germans run through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they called, is somebody a woodturner?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
